Bonnie Wright https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bonnie_Wright 0 Bonnie Francesca Wright (born 17 February 1991) is an English actress, film director, screenwriter, model and producer. She is best known for playing the role of Ginny Weasley in the Harry Potter film series, based on the novel series of the same name by J. K. Rowling.
